				  <tr>
					<td align="left" valign="top" class="art_content"><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 24.1pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">&nbsp;因</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">单位</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">发展和教学科研工作的需要，</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">经学校批准，四川大学物理科学与技术学院</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">现面向海内外公开招聘</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">教学科研</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">岗位人员，相关事宜如下：</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><br />
</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><br />
</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">一</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">、招聘岗位</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><br />
</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">教学科研</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">岗</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">:</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">1</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">人</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><br />
</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><br />
</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">二、</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">岗位职责</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><br />
</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 24.1pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">&nbsp;1</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">.</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">积极参与岗位职责要求的各项工作；</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">完成四川大学</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">相应</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">岗位的年工作量</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">；</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 24.1pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">&nbsp;2.</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">积极参加各种学术活动，</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">参加国际交流；</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">积极申报并承担国家、四川省和我校的各级各类科研项目</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">；</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 24.1pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">&nbsp;3.积极参与校、院两级公共事务；</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">　</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">完成</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">学校、</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">学院交办的其他</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">各项</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">工作。&nbsp;</span><!--EndFragment--></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 24.1pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><br />
</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">三、</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">招聘条件</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><br />
</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">1.</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">遵纪守法，热爱教育事业，</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">具有良好的思想道德素质和职业道德，身心健康</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">。</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 24.1pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">2.具备较强的团队合作精神和独立科研能力，已有高水平论文发表或有主持省级以上科研项目经历者优先。</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 24.1pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">3.</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">具有国内外高水平大学博士学位，</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">年龄35岁以下<span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">，原则上具有1年及以上海外经历。</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 24.1pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000"><!--EndFragment--></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left; margin-left: 21pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-para-margin-left: 2.0000gd; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">四、</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">招聘程序</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><br />
</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">1.应聘人员登录四川大学人事信息管理系统（</span><span><a onfocus="undefined" href="http://rsxxgl.scu.edu.cn/Common/Recruitment.aspx"><span style="font-family: 新宋体; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; text-decoration: underline; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; text-underline: single">http://rsxxgl.scu.edu.cn/Common/Recruitment.aspx</span></a></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">），填写个人应聘申请</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">；</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">注册时请提供准确的个人信息，因个人信息不实造成的后果由应聘者本人承担</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt">。</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><br />
</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">2.由</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">单位</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">招聘工作领导小组对应聘人员进行甄选，确定参加面试人员名单。</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><br />
</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">3.由</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">单位</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">教授委员会专家</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">和相关部处人员对候选人进</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">行面试，择优确定拟聘人员。</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: 'yes'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><br />
